## Install

Lambda:

- Run `pip install slack_bolt -t .`.
- Zip repo and upload to Lambda.
- Add environmental variables `SLACK_BOT_TOKEN` and `SLACK_SIGNING_SECRET` from slack app.
- Run `curl -X POST https://slack.com/api/auth.test \-H "Authorization: Bearer xoxb-your-oauth-token"` and add the team id as an enviromental variable `SLACK_TEAM_ID`.

Triggers:

- Add new EventBridge with schedule `cron(0 13 ? * MON-FRI 1,3)`.

Dynamodb:

- Create table `intros` with partition column `channel` and sort column `date`.
- Create index `is_latest_date-channel-index` with partition column `is_latest_date` and sort column `channel`.
